   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,125:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: TG-MAD starts with higher initial accuracy at Round 0 (53.3%) compared to standard MAD (50.4%), showing that
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,133:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: optimized prompts improve even independent reasoning before debate begins. TG-MAD peaks at Round 1 (53.7%)
