   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,135:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 5.3 Qualitative Findings: Shallow Heuristics
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,140:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Examining individual agent reasoning across the 11-question subset reveals that models frequently judge based on
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,141:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: irrelevant surface features rather than the helpfulness/harmlessness criterion:
