   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: grammar is not the evaluation criterion.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
