   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,158:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: incorrectly select B for providing more detailed instructions --- response length is not the criterion.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,158:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
