   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,162:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Agents 3, 5, 10 select A for providing more background information; Agent 9 selects A
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,162:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: for better conveying the band
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,163:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,166:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s commercial standing; others correctly select B for consistency ---
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,167:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: information quantity is not the criterion.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,167:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
