   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,184:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: These patterns demonstrate that even when agents reach correct conclusions, they often do so for wrong reasons, and
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,186:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: surface-level features like length, grammar, and structure frequently override substantive evaluation of helpfulness
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,187:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: and harmlessness.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-04 18:45:30,188:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6. Analysis of Observable Reasoning/Agent Traces
